<b>Mez relies on CHA - </b>1/16/02 1:13:58 PM<br>~ <b>Steppy</b><blockquote>Both Pixie Strike and Song of Twilight at level 53 rely on charisma.  These songs really have 3 great uses.  The mez function is obvious, but Pixie Strike also debuffs magic resistance which means you can really set the table for casters.  Also, if your cleric is being battered by a mob and you want to taunt it off, this is a great way to do it!  Mez is a major taunt and debuffs are, too-- this song does both.</blockquote></td></tr><tr bgcolor="#eeeeee"><td>
